PKILL

&2Pkill&n

&3Usage:&n  &4pkill enable&n

This is the command to enable you to join the violent world of player
killing.  Once enabled you will find yourself with a permanent &4(PK)&n
flag against your name.  If you are not a member of a clan this is not
reversible.  So be very careful setting it if you do not want to join
a clan as not many gods will remove this flag for you.
