       drop all.<object>
       drop all
       drop <number> coins&n

If you lose interest in a carried item, you can drop it on the ground.

Example:
  > drop bottle
  > drop all.bread
  > drop all
  > drop 1000 coins

See also: DONATE, GET, JUNK
