EMOTE :

&2Emote :&n

&3Usage:&n &4emote <message>
       : <message>&n

Show people what you're feeling.  The shorthand is ":".
Your name will be displayed followed by the string.

Example:

If your name is "Helt",

  > emote is feeling very sad today.

will display:

Helt is feeling very sad today.

See also: SOCIALS
