INFO

&2Info&n

&3Usage:&n  &4info <playername>&n

This command will give you basic information about the player you requested, like
level, class and what social ranking he has.  Also it will show you their email, 
webpage or personal details if they have been added.

To add email webpage or personal:

&3usage:&n &4info <email | webpage | personal> <details>&n

This requires a save after you have done this.
