SKILLINFO SPELLINFO

&2Skillinfo Spellinfo&n

&3Usage:&n &4skillinfo <class> <race>&n
	   &4spellinfo <class> <race>&n

These two commands are usefull to find out what a combination of
class and race will receive on the spells/skills. You only need to
type either skillinfo or spellinfo and they will bring up the same 
listing.  Anything listed in red is completely unobtainable for the
combination of class and race you have selected.  This is also a 
handy tool when deciding what you want to remort too as you will see
what skills and spells you will receive on each remort class.

If you are wanting particular information on a spell or skill alone 
the usage would be:

&4skillinfo (spellinfo) <'spell/skill name'> <race>&n

This will show you the classes the skill/spell is available too and the
classes that are in red are the ones that will not get the spell/skill.
