WHERE

&2Where&n

&3Usage:&n &4where <mob | player | object>&n

Tells you the location of a mob, player or object.

Mortals can only "where" mob or players from within the zone they are in.

Immortals may type 'where' without arguments to see where everybody is and
also locate objects using the where command.


