when you login.  If you miss it at login, just use this command!
#
MURDER

&2Murder&n

&3Usage:&n &4murder <victim>&n

Murder command is used to hit another player, to avoid accidental flagging (i.e.
trying to type "kiss Nia" but accidentally typing "kill Nia").

Note that it is illegal to kill other players in any circumstances other than
those specified in the POLICY statement.  If you try and kill players outside designated
pkzones you will get a KILLER flag.  If you are flagged as a killer, you are unable to do
damage and other players will be allowed to use the MURDER command to
kill you without being flagged themselves.

See also: FLAGS AREAS POLICY
