PRACTICE PRACTISE

&2Practice&n

&3Usage:&n &4practice <skill | spell>&n

Practice is the way you improve your spells and skills.  You can only do
so in your guild, where your guildmaster can help you train.
You can only practice a certain amount for each level you gain.  
Unused practice sessions will accumulate for use in future levels.

If you type practice without arguments anywhere other than in your guild, 
you will get a list of all of the spells and skills available to you
and your level of proficiency at each.
